```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant UI as Streamlit UI
    participant SF as Service Factory
    participant GS as Gemini Service
    participant DB as SQLite
    participant API as Gemini API

    User->>UI: Enter prompt & click Run
    UI->>SF: get_services()
    SF->>GS: generate(system, user, config)
    GS->>API: generate_content()
    API-->>GS: Response text
    GS-->>UI: PromptRunResponse
    UI->>SF: experiments.create()
    SF->>DB: INSERT experiment
    UI->>SF: analytics.record_event()
    SF->>DB: INSERT analytics
    UI-->>User: Display response
```
